title: one
body:
<<avatar nerd>> Yo! Ivan on tech is that you?
<<avatar ivan>> Yes man. It's me but don't tell anyone!
<<avatar nerd>> But why are you wearing this?
<<avatar ivan>> I am disguised man, don't want to attract much attention
<<avatar nerd>> Okay!
<<avatar ivan >> I heard you are building on ethereum and trying to combine financial products and nft
<<avatar nerd>> Yeah!
<<avatar ivan>> Can I join the nerd gang as an advisor?
<<avatar nerd>> Absolutely man, you are a true nerd!
<<avatar ivan>> Be careful of the Haunted Big strong guys... These HAUNTED exchange owners are everywhere!!

title: two
body:
<<avatar nerd>> CZ, is that you? Damn! You have changed
<<avatar nerd>> You were such a cool Nerd back in the day...  
<<avatar cz>> I am not your friend CZ, I took his soul and now i have his body! 
<<avatar cz>> Now, give me your precious NERD tokens or you would be next
<<avatar nerd>> i'm not scared of you so i'm not giving you shit
<<avatar nerd>> Liquidity is locked on Uniswap! 
<<avatar cz>> Poor little Nerd!
<<avatar cz>> You don't understand, do you?
<<avatar cz>> I have a whole Haunted army! so you can never win
<<avatar nerd>> Let's see about that

title: three
body:
<<avatar nerd>> Sam, is that you?
<<avatar sam>> You stupid Nerd!
<<avatar sam>> This is not your nerd-y friend Sam!
<<avatar sam>> I told you i took his soul and i am using his body!
<<avatar nerd>> Shame on you!
<<avatar nerd>> Sam was one of my ultimate nerd idols...
<<avatar nerd>> He also had a great hair and a very good exchange.
<<avatar nerd>> I don't know what you are, but i will defeat you
<<avatar nerd>> And save all my Nerd-y friends!
<<avatar sam>> You've got no idea what you are going up against!
<<avatar nerd>> And you have no idea about the nerd community!
<<avatar nerd>> We have code!
<<avatar nerd>> We have memes
<<avatar nerd>> We have degen farmers!
<<avatar nerd>> And we are growing everyday!
